CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: McGraw Hill is a leading global provider of information solutions for education across K-12 to higher education, and through professional learning. We harness the power of content, data-driven insights, and learning science to deliver personalized learning experiences and drive positive outcomes throughout the entire learning lifecycle. On an annual basis, we serve approximately 60 million learners and educators.
